    <item>
      <title>特朗普准备提名福尔肯德担任财政部副部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/trump-poised-to-pick-faulkender-as-deputy-treasury-secretary</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普准备任命金融学教授迈克尔·福肯德 (Michael Faulkender) 担任财政部副部长，福肯德在其第一任总统任期内实施了一项重要的疫情时期救助计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/trump-poised-to-pick-faulkender-as-deputy-treasury-secretary</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 17:01:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普财政部长将与共和党参议员会面，讨论美联储和关税问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/bessent-to-meet-with-gop-s-thune-with-fed-and-tariffs-on-agenda</link>
      <description><![CDATA[即将上任的参议院共和党领袖约翰·图恩表示，他预计将在提名听证会前讨论财政部长提名人斯科特·贝森特对关税和美联储的看法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/bessent-to-meet-with-gop-s-thune-with-fed-and-tariffs-on-agenda</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 16:54:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>智利国会为博里奇赢得胜利，成立公共安全部</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/chile-congress-creates-public-security-ministry-in-win-for-boric</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利国会最终批准了成立公共安全部的法案，这对总统加布里埃尔·博里奇来说是一项胜利，他的政府将加大打击犯罪的力度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/chile-congress-creates-public-security-ministry-in-win-for-boric</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 16:40:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普任命彼得·纳瓦罗为贸易和制造业顾问</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/trump-taps-peter-navarro-as-trade-and-manufacturing-counselor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普任命彼得·纳瓦罗为其贸易和制造业高级顾问，将这位曾被监禁的顾问提升回与上一届特朗普政府中类似的职位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/trump-taps-peter-navarro-as-trade-and-manufacturing-counselor</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 16:12:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克总统警告抗议活动可能导致工人工资延迟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/mozambique-president-warns-protests-risk-pay-delays-for-workers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫桑比克总统警告说，针对 10 月 9 日有争议的选举的持续抗议活动正在增加公务员工资延迟发放的风险，因为骚乱影响了税收收入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/mozambique-president-warns-protests-risk-pay-delays-for-workers</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 16:11:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Sheinbaum 的团队声称墨西哥高速公路安全计划取得了进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/sheinbaum-s-team-claims-gains-under-mexico-highway-security-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥总统克劳迪娅·谢因鲍姆加强国家高速公路安全的努力正在取得成效，初步估计显示，在她执政的最初几周里，货物盗窃案有所减少]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/sheinbaum-s-team-claims-gains-under-mexico-highway-security-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 16:06:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普选择曾进行过私人太空行走的亿万富翁来领导 NASA</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/trump-picks-jared-isaacman-as-nasa-administrator</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他将提名金融科技亿万富翁、资深 SpaceX 宇航员贾里德·艾萨克曼担任下一任 NASA 局长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/trump-picks-jared-isaacman-as-nasa-administrator</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 16:05:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马赫卢夫称地缘政治风险加剧对爱尔兰不利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/increased-geopolitical-risks-negative-for-ireland-makhlouf-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱尔兰央行行长周三表示，爱尔兰面临的地缘政治风险异常大，跨国公司数量庞大，对国内经济至关重要。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/increased-geopolitical-risks-negative-for-ireland-makhlouf-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 15:45:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塔克·卡尔森就乌克兰战争采访俄罗斯外交部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/trump-ally-carlson-in-moscow-interviews-lavrov-on-war-in-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[媒体名人塔克·卡尔森是当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的一位有影响力的盟友，他表示，在人们对新一届美国政府计划迅速结束乌克兰战争的猜测中，他已在莫斯科采访了俄罗斯外交部长谢尔盖·拉夫罗夫。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/trump-ally-carlson-in-moscow-interviews-lavrov-on-war-in-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 15:28:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普将在长岛福克斯国家活动上接受奖项</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/trump-will-receive-award-at-fox-news-ceremony-on-long-island</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普将于周四前往家乡纽约州，参加由福克斯新闻频道合作的在线流媒体平台 Fox Nation 主办的年度颁奖典礼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/trump-will-receive-award-at-fox-news-ceremony-on-long-island</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 04:24:59 GMT</pubDate>
